ALGORITHM FOR CHESSBOARD WHEN GIVEN TWO POSITIONS AS INPUT, RETURN TRUE IF THEY HAVE SAME COLOUR ELSE FALSE

Step-1:Begin
Step-2:Enter the first row "r1"
Step-3:Enter the second row "r2"
Step-4:Enter the first column "c1"
Step-5:Enter the second column "c2"
Step-6:Now take sum of first and second rows and columns (sum=r1+r2+c1+c2)
Step-7:sum%2==0
Step-8:If sum%2==0 then print True else print False
Step-9:End
